83
00:06:48,420 --> 00:06:53,460
Now, players can make money inside the games, so most of that money wasn't spent from actual players' wallets,

84
00:06:53,460 --> 00:06:55,860
but still, that's a lot of subscription time.

85
00:06:55,860 --> 00:06:58,280
But real money is constantly going into these games.

86
00:06:58,280 --> 00:07:03,840
Players routinely sell, buy, and trade gaming aspects from this game and others, even though it's forbidden.

87
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:06,820
This is on top of the subscription, or pay-to-play business models.

88
00:07:06,820 --> 00:07:11,000
